CREATE DATABASE spaceInvaders

CREATE TABLE spaceinvaders.Tbl_Poderes ( 
  Num_Id_Poderes INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT , 
  Num_Cantidad_Poderes INT NOT NULL , 
  PRIMARY KEY ( `Num_Id_Poderes` ) 
) ENGINE=InnoDB

CREATE TABLE `spaceinvaders`.`Tbl_Imagen` (
  `Num_Id_Imagen` INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
  `Img_Imagen_Imagen` BLOB NOT NULL ,
  PRIMARY KEY ( `Num_Id_Imagen` )
) ENGINE=InnoDB


CREATE TABLE `spaceinvaders`.`Tbl_Tipo`(
  `Num_Id_Tipo` INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
  Num_DisparoImagen_Tipo int,
  key (Num_DisparoImagen_Tipo),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_DisparoImagen_Tipo) REFERENCES `spaceinvaders`.`Tbl_Imagen`( `Num_Id_Imagen` ) on update cascade,
  Num_Id_Imagen int,
  key (Num_Id_Imagen),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_Id_Imagen) REFERENCES spaceinvaders.Tbl_Imagen( `Num_Id_Imagen` ) on update cascade,
  PRIMARY KEY ( `Num_Id_Tipo` ) 
) ENGINE=InnoDB


create table spaceinvaders.Tbl_Personaje( 
  Num_Id_Personaje int not null auto_increment primary key, 
  Num_IdDisparo_Imagen int,
  key (Num_IdDisparo_Imagen),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_IdDisparo_Imagen) references spaceinvaders.Tbl_Imagen(Num_Id_Imagen) on update cascade, 
  Num_Id_Imagen int,
  key (Num_Id_Imagen),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_Id_Imagen) references spaceinvaders.Tbl_Imagen(Num_Id_Imagen) on update cascade, 
  Num_Vidas_Personaje int not null 
) ENGINE=InnoDB


CREATE TABLE spaceinvaders.Tbl_Invasores( 
  Num_Id_Invasores INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  Num_Id_Tipo int,
  key (Num_Id_Tipo), 
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_Id_Tipo) REFERENCES spaceinvaders.Tbl_Tipo(Num_Id_Tipo) on update cascade, 
  PRIMARY KEY ( `Num_Id_Invasores` ) 
) ENGINE=InnoDB



CREATE TABLE spaceinvaders.Tbl_Mundo (
  Num_Id_Mundo int,
  Num_Id_Imagen int,
  key (Num_Id_Imagen),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_Id_Imagen) references spaceinvaders.Tbl_Imagen(Num_Id_Imagen) on update cascade,
  Num_Velocidad_Mundo int NOT NULL,
  Num_Id_Poderes int,
  key (Num_Id_Poderes),
  FOREIGN KEY (Num_Id_Poderes) references spaceinvaders.Tbl_Poderes(Num_Id_Poderes) on update cascade,
  PRIMARY KEY (Num_Id_Mundo)
) ENGINE=InnoDB



CREATE TABLE spaceinvaders.Tbl_Ranking (
  Str_Jugador_Ranking varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  Num_Pocision_Ranking int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  Num_Puntaje_Ranking int(200) NOT NULL, 
  PRIMARY KEY (Num_Pocision_Ranking)
) ENGINE=InnoDB;

CREATE TRIGGER tales AFTER INSERT ON blabla
FOR EACH ROW
IF NEW.id = '1' THEN
    INSERT INTO codigo_ganador (`id`) VALUES (NEW.id);
END IF;
END;

CREATE TRIGGER tales AFTER INSERT ON ranking
FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
   DELETE FROM `spaceinvaders`.`ranking` WHERE `ranking`.`posicion` > 11;  
END;







drop trigger expire_trigger;


  CREATE TRIGGER expire_trigger
    BEFORE INSERT ON ranking
    FOR EACH ROW BEGIN
    IF NEW.posicion > 7 THEN
        DELETE FROM ranking where posicion > 7;
    END IF;
    END;





drop procedure leeemp();
CREATE PROCEDURE leeemp()
BEGIN
SELECT COUNT( imagen.id )
FROM spaceinvaders.imagen AS imagen;
END;


CREATE PROCEDURE limpiar ()
    DELETE FROM ranking where posicion > 11;
